Package controller.commands

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CommandInterface<T>
    Given interface contains summary of the methods performed on the commands.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Brighten<T extends ModelInterface>
    This command is manage the brightness of the image.
    ColorTransformations<T extends EnhancedModelInterface>
    This command apply color transformation on the image.
    Combine<T extends ModelInterface>
    Given command is used to combine provided grey scale images of channel red, green and blue.
    Dither<T extends EnhancedModelInterface>
    Given command dither the image provided.
    Filter<T extends EnhancedModelInterface>
    Given command applies various filter on the image like blur and sharpening.
    FlipHorizontal<T extends ModelInterface>
    Given command flip the image horizontally.
    FlipVertical<T extends ModelInterface>
    Given command flip the image vertically.
    Load<T extends ModelInterface>
    Given command load the image into the hashmap.
    Save<T extends ModelInterface>
    Given command will save the image on the file path provided in the given file type.
    Split<T extends ModelInterface>
    Given command split provided image into red, green and blue greyscale image.
    VisualizeComponent<T extends ModelInterface>
    Given command convert into greyscale image according to the channel component provided.
